info.name: Message Refiner UAT
info.description: A collection of 5 requests intended to demonstrate the functionality of the DIBBs Message Refiner service. These requests test the various section-based and condition-based filtering options available through the service, showing them in isolation and in combination on a variety of data. This collection also shows how clinical services related to a particular SNOMED code are queried behind the scenes using the Trigger Code Reference Service. All data featured in these requests comes from anonymized case reports supplied by LAC's Department of Public Health.
